Reads and writes clinical-trial datasets losslessly across SAS XPORT (XPT), CDISC Dataset-JSON, and Apache Parquet, applying a specification to produce submission-ready SDTM and ADaM datasets. A single canonical metadata model carries labels, CDISC data types, lengths, SAS display formats, controlled-terminology references, and sort keys identically across every format, so conversion between any two formats is lossless by construction. Pure R and lightweight, with no external 'SAS' or 'Java' runtime.
